headline: Fox Corporation President and Chief Operating Officer John Nallen to Participate in Upcoming Deutsche Bank's 33rd Annual Media, Internet & Telecom Conference
summary: Fox Corporation (Nasdaq: FOXA, FOX) today announced that President and Chief Operating Officer John Nallen will participate in Deutsche Bank's 33rd Annual Media, Internet & Telecom Conference on Monday, March 10, at approximately 9:40am (Eastern), 6:40am (Pacific).
